OL,3,CRob Burrow made the world a better
OL,4,Cplace to be, says wife Lindsey
OL,6,FThe wife of Rob Burrow has said he
OL,7,F"made the world a better place to be".
OL,9,FIn a moving tribute, Lindsey Burrow
OL,10,Fsaid her husband had given "so many
OL,11,Fpeople hope" and had left an
OL,12,F"incredible" legacy.
OL,14,FEx-rugby league player Burrow died at
OL,15,Fthe age of 41 after a four-and-a-half-
OL,16,Fyear battle with motor neurone disease.
OL,18,FIn a first look video from BBC
OL,19,FBreakfast's interview, Mrs Burrow said
OL,20,Fit had been "overwhelming" to see all
OL,21,Fof the tributes paid to Rob.
