OL,3,CRob Burrow made the world a better
OL,4,Cplace to be, says wife Lindsey
OL,6,FBurrow spent his entire rugby league
OL,7,Fcareer with Leeds Rhinos and helped
OL,8,Fthem win eight Super League titles.
OL,10,FTwo years after his retirement in
OL,11,F2017, Burrow revealed his MND
OL,12,Fdiagnosis and began fundraising and
OL,13,Fcampaigning to raise awareness of the
OL,14,Fdisease and to improve care and
OL,15,Fresearch.
OL,17,FBurrow was made an MBE in the 2021 New
OL,18,FYear Honours list for his services to
OL,19,Frugby league and the MND community and
OL,20,Fwas promoted to a CBE in the 2024 New
OL,21,FYear Honours.
